Class TypeInferringNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jsimpledb.parse.expr.TypeInferringNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LambdaNode, MethodReferenceNode

    public abstract class TypeInferringNode
extends Object
implements Node
    Support superclass for Nodes that perform type inferrence and therefore require a target type in order to be completely parsed.
